<p>
<p>Suppose we have a scatterplot of variable X and variable Y. The scatterplot contains an outlier. The outlier greatly affects the slope of the regression line, in other words, the regression line changes when the outlier is removed. Choose the best answer.</p>
</p>]]></text>
